<title>Protests in Nicaragua</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Nicaragua&amp;#39;s suppression forces &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/may/31/nicaragua-peace-talks-daniel-ortega-abandoned-mothers-day-protest&#34;&gt;killed 11 more protesters&lt;/a&gt; in a massive demonstration led by mothers of protesters previously killed.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
