<title>Climate of &#34;fear and anxiety&#34; at NASA</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; NASA has a climate of &amp;quot;fear and anxiety&amp;quot; resulting from  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/science/2018/may/30/nasa-climate-change-sensitive-subject-since-trump-former-employee&#34;&gt;censorship about global heating&lt;/a&gt; which came straight from the cheater. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; This, I expect, is exactly what &lt;a href=&#34;https://stallman.org/glossary.html#cheater&#34;&gt;the cheater&lt;/a&gt; wants.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
